sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
    participant Controller as ODH Model Controller
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway
    participant Authorino as Authorino<br/>50051/TCP gRPC mTLS
    participant ISVC as InferenceService Pod<br/>mTLS
    participant Storage as Model Storage<br/>S3/PVC

    rect rgb(230, 240, 255)
        Note over User,Controller: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation (KServe Serverless)
        User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply InferenceService<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch event<br/>TLS 1.3 + ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create OpenShift Route<br/>TLS 1.3 + ServiceAccount
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create NetworkPolicy<br/>Pod isolation rules
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create PeerAuthentication<br/>mTLS STRICT mode
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Telemetry<br/>Istio observability
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>Prometheus scraping
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create AuthConfig (if auth enabled)<br/>Authorino JWT validation
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Update ServiceMeshMemberRoll<br/>Add namespace to mesh
    end

    rect rgb(255, 240, 230)
        Note over User,Storage: Flow 2: External Model Inference Request
        User->>Router: POST /v1/models/model:predict<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Router->>Gateway: Forward via VirtualService<br/>TLS (mesh)

        alt Auth Enabled
            Gateway->>Authorino: Validate JWT<br/>50051/TCP gRPC mTLS
            Authorino-->>Gateway: Auth decision
        end

        Gateway->>ISVC: Inference Request<br/>HTTP/gRPC over mTLS
        ISVC->>Storage: Load model artifacts<br/>443/TCP HTTPS (S3) or local PVC
        Storage-->>ISVC: Model data
        ISVC-->>Gateway: Prediction result
        Gateway-->>Router: Response
        Router-->>User: JSON response
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over Controller,ISVC: Flow 3: Monitoring Metrics Collection
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor/PodMonitor
        K8sAPI->>K8sAPI: Prometheus Operator reconciles
        Note over ISVC: Prometheus scrapes<br/>metrics via ServiceMonitor
    end
